{"tid":2316800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女子涉雷射筆射警眼一秒罪成 求情指抑鬱入獄或加重病情 鄭紀航：邊個坐監精神冇損害？","createTime":"2020-12-08T06:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T08:27:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91914b1e5e6015db4783affea0c6490d83bf051a","tid":2316800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"警方去年萬聖節晚上在中環蘭桂坊一帶實施人群管理，其間一名年輕女子被指用雷射筆射向一名高級督察眼睛一秒，隨後被捕。她否認襲警、非法集結及在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品三罪。裁判官鄭紀航今早聽過雙方結案陳詞後，即日裁定涉案女子三罪成立。辯方求情時呈上精神科醫生報告，指被告受事件影響，患上抑鬱及創傷後遺症，如判處監禁式刑罰，會對她的精神造成更大損害。惟鄭官聞言謂：「我想知邊個判坐監， 精神係冇損害嘅呢？」鄭官將於下午判刑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/K4JJJW6ENVGV5HICRWQMSFD6NI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FK4JJJW6ENVGV5HICRWQMSFD6NI%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7GrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=789344ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FK4JJJW6ENVGV5HICRWQMSFD6NI%2F&h=8f189a5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/K4JJJW6ENVGV5HICRWQMSFD6NI/</a>"},{"pid":"922fb00a0700aa22c7b8d7cbede7ae8aeb5c5795","tid":2316800,"uid":291936,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"又真係無講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302800142fb7e269581fe828f112646db3ac4e69","tid":2316800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"450aa5e4c29cad2e70f1182815a9f90da6232859","tid":2316800,"uid":107656,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"922fb00a0700aa22c7b8d7cbede7ae8aeb5c5795","tid":2316800,"uid":291936,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"又真係無講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor